# 🚀 ReachIQ — AI-Native Mini CRM

ReachIQ is an AI-powered Customer Relationship Management system built for intelligent marketing automation. It enables marketers to create, execute, and analyze campaigns using natural language commands powered by AI.

📌 Overview

Traditional CRM systems require manual effort for segmentation, messaging, and campaign tracking.  
ReachIQ solves this by introducing an **AI Campaign Agent** that transforms plain English instructions into fully executable marketing campaigns.

 ✨ Features

 🤖 AI Campaign Agent
- Create campaigns using natural language
- Automatic customer segmentation
- AI-generated personalized messages
- Campaign scoring and reasoning

🧠 Smart Audience Engine
- Filters customers based on:
  - City
  - Spending behavior
  - Inactivity period

 📊 Live Dashboard
- Total revenue
- Customer reach
- Conversion rate
- Active campaigns

📡 Real-Time Campaign Tracking
- Sent → Delivered → Opened → Clicked lifecycle
- Live activity stream updates

 📋 Campaign History
- Full audit logs
- Audience segmentation details
- Message templates used
- Individual recipient tracking
 👥 Customer Module
- 500+ realistic customer dataset
- Advanced filtering system

 📈 Analytics Module
- Funnel analysis
- Channel performance comparison
- City-wise engagement insights


🏗️ Architecture

- Frontend: Next.js (React-based UI)
- Backend APIs: Next.js API Routes
- AI Engine: Gemini 1.5 Flash
- Data Layer:JSON-based storage (portable design)
- Deployment:Vercel

🔄 Workflow

1. User enters campaign goal in natural language  
2. AI (Gemini) generates:
   - Audience segment
   - Message template
   - Channel recommendation
3. Campaign is launched via API
4. Channel Service simulates delivery
5. CRM receives callbacks and updates UI in real time

 ⚙️ API Structure

- `/api/campaigns/launch` → Launch campaign
- `/api/campaigns/history` → Campaign logs
- `/api/customers` → Customer data
- `/api/metrics` → Analytics data

 🧠 AI Integration

ReachIQ uses structured prompting with Gemini:

- Converts natural language → JSON workflow
- Ensures consistent segmentation logic
- Provides confidence scores & reasoning

Fallback rule-based system ensures reliability when AI is unavailable.

 🚀 Deployment

Deployed on Vercel:https://xeno-assignment-beus.vercel.app/campaign
